{"tid":1802894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稱多人不滿大學校長處理方式 威脅減撥款 楊潤雄：並非不可能","createTime":"2019-12-29T19:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T14:40:23.000Z","uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb4d4d442ee4b0d0ddbddac4be35dcedff94c91","tid":1802894,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:31:26.000Z","msg":"反修例運動中，大專生成為前綫抗爭主將，警方更多次污名化大學為「兵工廠」，建制派更借詞反對大學撥款。教育局局長楊潤雄在接受內地媒體《上觀新聞》專訪時稱，要調整對大學的撥款並非不可能，但撥款牽涉各方面，包括要考慮大學有多少學生及研究項目，而調整撥款會否影響大學的研究及學生教育。<br />\n<br />\n中文大學及理工大學上月被警方圍攻，並施放多枚催淚彈，校園不少設施須時間及金錢復修。記者在訪問中稱社會有意見批評學校被破壞得千瘡百孔，「卻又伸手向政府要錢修復，很多人覺得這似乎不太合理。」楊潤雄稱，香港過去幾10年來從沒有面對過破壞規模如此大的事件，更指摘大學校長在處理方式上，「確實讓很多人不滿意」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191229/60429921\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F60429921&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK92CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=dcc94260\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191229%2F60429921&h=d1827fe7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191229/60429921</a>"},{"pid":"90de80778fe842c20d6b645bbb23b70eb00b9441","tid":1802894,"uid":200958,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:41:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"566f429ed65160f175d4f6273984e25e88703655","tid":1802894,"uid":34436,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:45:29.000Z","msg":"黑警過度武力打鳩市民，「卻又伸手向市民要錢出糧，很多人覺得這完全不合理。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275e4eeaafb56ec92cee7648c851c0d2c57e80f2","tid":1802894,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"566f429ed65160f175d4f6273984e25e88703655","tid":1802894,"uid":34436,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:45:29.000Z","msg":"黑警過度武力打鳩市民，「卻又伸手向市民要錢出糧，很多人覺得這完全不合理。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:50:19.000Z","msg":"咪就係囉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c1517fbd833f2996255e0d1fc7b841723c363f","tid":1802894,"uid":212843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:53:49.000Z","msg":"關你撚事教局<br />\n立法會話事㗎"},{"pid":"997a96687275c4b42a9a02276a48b3d52dca0ada","tid":1802894,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:53:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">楊潤雄快死仔</span>"},{"pid":"a921425f967ff80e1e6f5d8851237244a7c1ec9e","tid":1802894,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"566f429ed65160f175d4f6273984e25e88703655","tid":1802894,"uid":34436,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:45:29.000Z","msg":"黑警過度武力打鳩市民，「卻又伸手向市民要錢出糧，很多人覺得這完全不合理。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T19:54:42.000Z","msg":"不滿黑警既人比不滿大學多十倍"},{"pid":"19ca8faf3cbdea43f29fc345a5d88a6ad98f93a0","tid":1802894,"uid":8461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T23:13:36.000Z","msg":"立法會7月1日被警方圍攻，並施放多枚催淚彈，立法會不少設施須時間及金錢復修。記者在訪問中稱社會有意見批評立法會被破壞得千瘡百孔，「卻又伸手向政府要錢修復，很多人覺得這似乎不太合理。」本人稱，香港過去幾10年來從沒有面對過破壞規模如此大的事件，更指摘立法會主席在處理方式上，「確實讓很多人不滿意」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46309a48e960bd20ab2e38b385448795725f1b3c","tid":1802894,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T01:14:55.000Z","msg":"整個民調會唔會多人不滿教育局長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}